## What's Working ✅

1. **Fallback chain** — ScrapingAnt is the most reliable provider (3/5 success)
2. **Tilesman extraction** — Simple supplier catalogs with clear HTML work
3. **PDF download** — Large files download successfully via fallback
4. **DB records** — 100 evidence records from 19 unique URLs already stored

## Prioritized Fix List

| Priority | Fix | Impact |
|----------|-----|--------|
| **P0** | Fix HTML-to-text cleanup before LLM extraction | Unblocks 50%+ of sources |
| **P0** | Increase content snippet to 32K chars | Better extraction from HTML |
| **P1** | Fix ScrapingDog config (add `dynamic=true`, 30s timeout) | Unblocks aggregator sites |
| **P1** | Add Firecrawl credit caching (skip for 24h when exhausted) | Faster retries |
| **P2** | Replace ArchDaily with RSS feed URL | 1 more source recoverable |
| **P2** | Add PDF text extraction (pdf-parse) for brochures | Unlocks developer intel |
| **P3** | Consider Firecrawl plan upgrade | Best quality scraping |
